  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375\u000729F.",
    "Cook Arabic rice according to package instructions.",
    "In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add ground beef and cook, breaking up with a spoon, until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add crushed tomatoes, onion, garlic, fennel, and cook, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in nimono sauce, and season with salt and pepper.",
    "In a large bowl, combine cooked rice, beef and vegetable mixture, mozzarella cheese, Parmesan cheese, and egg.",
    "Transfer mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Mix breadcrumbs and a pinch of salt in a small bowl, and sprinkle over top of Lasagna.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Let rest for 10 minutes before serving."
